bcl:text:
AND WHEREAS the Kunst'aa guu – Kunst'aayah Reconciliation Protocol represents an
        incremental step in the process of the reconciliation of the Haida and Crown
        titles;

AND WHEREAS the Kunst'aa guu – Kunst'aayah Reconciliation Protocol and the new
        relationship are intended by the Haida Nation and British Columbia to guide joint
        decision-making regarding land and natural resource management on Haida Gwaii;

AND WHEREAS the Kunst'aa guu – Kunst'aayah Reconciliation Protocol provides for the
        commitment of the parties to further refine and develop the processes for operational level
        decision-making on Haida Gwaii;

bcl:text.#text:
means the Haida Gwaii Management Council established as set
            out in section
              3;
